Class ProjectManagementOMRSTopicListener

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.repositoryservices.connectors.omrstopic.OMRSTopicListenerBase
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.projectmanagement.listener.ProjectManagementOMRSTopicListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
OMRSTopicListener, OMRSTopicRepositoryEventListener
public class ProjectManagementOMRSTopicListener extends OMRSTopicListenerBase
ProjectManagementOMRSTopicListener received details of each OMRS event from the cohorts that the local server is connected to. It passes NEW_ENTITY_EVENTs to the publisher.
